---
// Bad vs good crystal PCB layout — showing trace length, guard ring, and other signals.
---
<div class="not-prose grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2">
  <figure class="rounded-lg border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 p-3">
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-rose-700">BAD — 긴 트레이스, 가드 없음</div>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 320 220" class="mt-2 w-full">
      <rect x="1" y="1" width="318" height="218" fill="#fff" stroke="#e2e8f0" />

      <!-- MCU -->
      <rect x="20" y="80" width="60" height="60" fill="#0f172a" />
      <text x="32" y="115" font-size="9" fill="#fff" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">MCU</text>
      <text x="82" y="98" font-size="8" fill="#22d3a5" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">XIN</text>
      <text x="82" y="128" font-size="8" fill="#fbbf24" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">XOUT</text>

      <!-- Crystal — far away -->
      <rect x="220" y="90" width="40" height="40" fill="#fff" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="1.2" />
      <text x="226" y="80" font-size="9" fill="#0f172a" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">Y1</text>

      <!-- Long winding traces -->
      <path d="M 80 95 L 120 95 L 120 60 L 200 60 L 200 100 L 220 100" fill="none" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <path d="M 80 125 L 130 125 L 130 160 L 210 160 L 210 120 L 220 120" fill="none" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="1.5" />

      <!-- Caps far from MCU -->
      <rect x="180" y="50" width="14" height="6" fill="#4f46e5" />
      <text x="180" y="46" font-size="8" fill="#4f46e5" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">C1</text>
      <rect x="180" y="170" width="14" height="6" fill="#4f46e5" />
      <text x="180" y="190" font-size="8" fill="#4f46e5" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">C2</text>

      <!-- Aggressor signal crossing nearby -->
      <line x1="100" y1="180" x2="290" y2="180" stroke="#fbbf24" stroke-width="2" />
      <text x="100" y="195" font-size="8" fill="#a16207" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">옆에 클럭/SPI 같은 noisy 신호</text>

      <!-- Highlight problems -->
      <text x="10" y="20" font-size="9" fill="#9f1239" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">긴 XIN/XOUT 트레이스 = 큰 stray</text>
      <text x="10" y="34" font-size="9" fill="#9f1239" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">옆에 noisy 신호 = jitter 픽업</text>
    </svg>
    <figcaption class="mt-1 text-xs text-rose-800">트레이스가 길수록 stray cap 증가, 옆 noisy 신호와 결합으로 jitter 발생.</figcaption>
  </figure>

  <figure class="rounded-lg border border-emerald-200 bg-emerald-50 p-3">
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-emerald-700">GOOD — 짧은 트레이스, 가드 링</div>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 320 220" class="mt-2 w-full">
      <rect x="1" y="1" width="318" height="218" fill="#fff" stroke="#e2e8f0" />

      <!-- MCU -->
      <rect x="20" y="80" width="60" height="60" fill="#0f172a" />
      <text x="32" y="115" font-size="9" fill="#fff" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">MCU</text>
      <text x="82" y="98" font-size="8" fill="#22d3a5" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">XIN</text>
      <text x="82" y="128" font-size="8" fill="#fbbf24" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">XOUT</text>

      <!-- Guard ring (GND outline around the whole crystal area) -->
      <rect x="88" y="62" width="100" height="96" fill="none" stroke="#10b981" stroke-width="2" stroke-dasharray="3 2" />
      <!-- Stitching vias on guard ring -->
      <circle cx="92"  cy="66"  r="2" fill="#10b981" />
      <circle cx="184" cy="66"  r="2" fill="#10b981" />
      <circle cx="92"  cy="154" r="2" fill="#10b981" />
      <circle cx="184" cy="154" r="2" fill="#10b981" />
      <circle cx="138" cy="62"  r="2" fill="#10b981" />
      <circle cx="138" cy="158" r="2" fill="#10b981" />
      <text x="92" y="58" font-size="8" fill="#047857" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">GND guard ring</text>

      <!-- Crystal — close -->
      <rect x="120" y="100" width="40" height="20" fill="#fff" stroke="#0f172a" stroke-width="1.2" />
      <text x="124" y="113" font-size="8" fill="#0f172a" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">Y1</text>

      <!-- Short traces -->
      <line x1="80" y1="95" x2="100" y2="95" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <line x1="100" y1="95" x2="100" y2="105" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <line x1="100" y1="105" x2="120" y2="105" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="1.5" />

      <line x1="80" y1="125" x2="100" y2="125" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <line x1="100" y1="125" x2="100" y2="115" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="1.5" />
      <line x1="100" y1="115" x2="120" y2="115" stroke="#059669" stroke-width="1.5" />

      <!-- Caps close -->
      <rect x="103" y="78" width="14" height="6" fill="#4f46e5" />
      <text x="106" y="74" font-size="8" fill="#4f46e5" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">C1</text>
      <rect x="103" y="138" width="14" height="6" fill="#4f46e5" />
      <text x="106" y="152" font-size="8" fill="#4f46e5" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">C2</text>

      <!-- Cap GND ties to guard -->
      <line x1="110" y1="78" x2="110" y2="66" stroke="#10b981" stroke-width="1" />
      <line x1="110" y1="144" x2="110" y2="154" stroke="#10b981" stroke-width="1" />

      <!-- Annotations -->
      <text x="10" y="20" font-size="9" fill="#065f46" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">짧은 트레이스 + 가드 링 + GND</text>
      <text x="10" y="34" font-size="9" fill="#065f46" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">밑면 plane 으로 stitched</text>

      <!-- "no signals" zone -->
      <text x="200" y="170" font-size="8" fill="#94a3b8" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">고속 신호는 멀리</text>
      <text x="200" y="184" font-size="8" fill="#94a3b8" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">(가드 영역 외부)</text>
    </svg>
    <figcaption class="mt-1 text-xs text-emerald-800">크리스탈 + 두 cap 을 가까이 모으고, GND guard ring + plane stitching via 로 격리.</figcaption>
  </figure>
</div>
